name: Wild Card Fantasy Baseball
blurb: Wild Card Fantasy Baseball is fantasy sports like you've never played them before. Power-Up cards!  Prize leagues!  FUN!

rewards.reward: Our eternal gratitude and the warm-fuzzy feeling that you helped the little guys take on and beat the Goliaths.
3 free card packs of your choosing to be used in-game

Limited-edition Wild Card Fantasy Baseball poster signed by the dev team, early beta access to all future Wild Card Fantasy Sports games (including listing as a beta tester in game credits), plus 10 free baseball card packs of your choosing to be used in-game!

A totally awesome limited-edition Wild Card Fantasy Baseball t-shirt, early beta access to all future Wild Card Fantasy Sports games (including listing as a beta tester in game credits), plus 25 free baseball card packs of your choosing to be used in-game!

A totally awesome limited-edition Wild Card Fantasy Baseball hoodie sweatshirt, early beta access to all future Wild Card Fantasy Sports games (including listing as a beta tester in game credits), plus 50 free baseball card packs of your choosing to be used in-game!

You can design your own limited edition card pack to be released in the game (includes listing as a guest designer in game credits), a totally awesome limited-edition Wild Card Fantasy Baseball hoodie sweatshirt, early beta access to all future Wild Card Fantasy Sports games (including listing as a beta tester in game credits), plus 50 free baseball card packs of your choosing to be used in-game!

2 tickets to any Major League baseball game you want (pending availability... although we do have connections), you can design your own limited edition card pack to be released in the game (includes listing as a guest designer in game credits), a totally awesome limited-edition Wild Card Fantasy Baseball hoodie sweatshirt, early beta access to all future Wild Card Fantasy Sports games (including listing as a beta tester in game credits), plus 50 free baseball card packs of your choosing to be used in-game!

The ultimate reward... we will rent out the party deck for a single Round Rock Express game and make you the guest of honor.  Your name will be on the scoreboard.  The crowd will cheer for you.  You and your companions will feel like the belles of the ball as we celebrate you with the entire city of Austin for one night.  You'll get all of the above as well.  Airfare and lodging not included.
